CommandPalette.html.title: CommandPalette

CommandPalette.html.description: Default options is litteraly const defaultOptions = { isShortcut: event => event.ctrlKey && event.altKey && event.key === 'p', navigationCallback(event) { switch (event.key) { case 'ArrowDown': this.next(); break; case 'ArrowUp': this.prev(); break; case 'Enter': this.dispatch(); break; } } }
